metadata.name: Alvord Sunset -ReGeneration Community #1 #1/21
metadata.description:
Title: Alvord Sunset -ReGeneration Community #1  
Edition: 21  
Artist: Dan Hawk  
License: Extended Editorial  
Resolution: 4000 x 2667

This is the sunset view on the Alvord Desert Playa, one of my favorite places on earth.  

This is one of the most unique places I've ever experienced- an ancient lakebed in the rain shadow of the Steens Mt in Remote SE Oregon. 

This art is part of the ReGeneration community and was gifted to the original holder as a token of appreciation for support.
